plot: A fresh new show about a couple of cute 9-year old boys, Jordan and Jayden Besana, aka JorJay, discussing their perspectives on the super bowl, Peyton Manning, Bruno Mars, Red Hot Chili Peppers and the Beatles.
title: The JorJay Show
